which
will
suggest
itself
to
him.
Nobody
in
the
house
will
be
self
possessed
but
you.
Now
promise
to
befriend
me
to
keep
Mr.
Sympson
away
from
me,
not
to
let
Henry
come
near,
lest
I
should
hurt
him.
Mind
mind
that
you
take
care
