yourself
too.
But
I
shall
not
injure
you;
I
know
I
shall
not.
Lock
the
chamber
door
against
the
surgeons;
turn
them
out
if
they
get
in.
Let
neither
the
young
nor
the
old
MacTurk
lay
a
