"I
promise
all
you
ask
without
comment,
without
reservation."
"If
female
help
is
needed,
call
in
my
housekeeper,
Mrs.
Gill.
Let
her
lay
me
out
if
I
die.
She
is
attached
to
me.
She
wronged
me
again
and
again,
and
again
and
again
I
forgave
her.
She
now
loves
me,
and
would
not
defraud
